{"tid":1382801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今場運動已到樽頸位，不過仲有得救！","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:35:55.000Z","uid":110332,"like":146,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"772e748ff0fe117210548a78f0be0c46290c0955","tid":1382801,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"首先！最重要係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣！</span></span> 因為我地 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">大量</span></span> 嘅文宣讓香港所有人感到同我地一樣嘅憤怒！！因為我地已經係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">命運共同體</span></span>！佢地同樣憤怒，之後前線<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做任何升級行動都好多人支持！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n文宣方向: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑社會=警察=港共政府</span></span> 以後可以直接話拒絕黑社會治港<br />\n<br />\n其次！同樣係因為我係命運共同體嘅關係，我地要避免自己成為 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">犬儒</span></span><br />\n(受到現實嘅潑冷水，由抗爭變到放棄，再到逆來順受，沉默) (依度有詳細解說，建議細睇<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2cMQAIp9kjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2cMQAIp9kjU&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=c1c7707f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2cMQAIp9kjU</a> )<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真正維穩係社會有大量犬儒</span></span> 我地千祈唔好灰心！唔好中計！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"575719136277cd30188f8def75d8bbbba28096ae","tid":1382801,"uid":78651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"利用狂犬症的黑警手上的催淚彈、橡膠子彈，送給大商家們嘗試下。當然不能少左工聯、民賤聯的總部"},{"pid":"6486f0f3adf5c320162c9c07f4d86f24f9376e6d","tid":1382801,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:25:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc7081c5fe450723f4972a4b69222cce72ef47fa","tid":1382801,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"